  -A, --auto-reference           output automatically generated references\n\
"));
        oputs_("ptx", gettext("\
  -G, --traditional              behave more like System V 'ptx'\n\
"));
        oputs_("ptx", gettext("\
  -F, --flag-truncation=STRING   use STRING for flagging line truncations.\n\
